      <Node id="77b34e19-39d9-494b-98ad-c8b1526e3a0c" name="CP-9 (3): SEPARATE STORAGE FOR CRITICAL INFORMATION" description="Critical information system software includes, for example, operating systems, cryptographic key management systems, and intrusion detection/prevention systems. Security-related information includes, for example, organizational inventories of hardware, software, and firmware components. Alternate storage sites typically serve as separate storage facilities for organizations." success="AND">
