      <Node id="04439115-e1c5-4523-b7ad-8bd6e5d7cf64" name="IA-2 (5): GROUP AUTHENTICATION" description="Requiring individuals to use individual authenticators as a second level of authentication helps organizations to mitigate the risk of using group authenticators." success="AND">
