  <Node id="2eaf25d7-6d01-47af-aef1-1366c471edf3" name="PE-20: ASSET MONITORING AND TRACKING" description="Asset location technologies can help organizations ensure that critical assets such as vehicles or essential information system components remain in authorized locations. Organizations consult with the Office of the General Counsel and the Senior Agency Official for Privacy (SAOP)/Chief Privacy Officer (CPO) regarding the deployment and use of asset location technologies to address potential privacy concerns." success="AND">
