      <Node id="fa173b54-a4ee-4199-a9a2-e8b268ae5c02" name="PL-4b." description="Receives a signed acknowledgment from such individuals, indicating that they have read, understand, and agree to abide by the rules of behavior, before authorizing access to information and the information system;" />
